Northrop Grumman Corp. was all but assured of winning the bid to acquire Ne=
wport News Shipbuilding Inc. as the Pentagon endorsed the deal and the Just=
ice Department, citing antitrust concerns, blocked a rival bid by General D=
ynamics Corp.=20
It marked a stunning turn of events for Northrop, which got the nod to acqu=
ire the Virginia builder of nuclear submarines and aircraft carriers despit=
e having been the underdog.=20
The Los Angeles-based defense contractor made an unsolicited offer for Newp=
ort News after the shipbuilder had inked a $2.1-billion deal with General D=
ynamics.=20
Separately, Northrop said third-quarter earnings fell 22% because of a larg=
e drop in pension fund investments.=20
