 to come.=20
Like many Internet pioneers, however, Kahle faces unfamiliar risks along wi=
th the opportunities: the archive might be the most massive violation of co=
pyright law since ownership rights over words came into being.=20
More than 10 billion pages are available at http://web.archive.org.=20
